title: O Dowd visits the site of £3.8million project at Ballymoney High School (Northern Ireland Executive) ...
text: ( Source : Northern Ireland Executive ) Education Minister John O'Dowd today visited the site of a £3.8million improvement project at Ballymoney High School . ~ Wednesday, 14 October 2015 The project includes a new two-storey modular building
